Miklos Says Bilateral Collateral Agreements Is No Solution

-- B y   R a d o s l a v   T o m e k
-- 
2011-08-18T13:36:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-18/miklos-says-bilateral-collateral-agreements-is-no-solution-1-.html
Slovak Finance Minister Ivan Miklos
said bilateral agreements on attaining collateral to aid  Greece 
is not a solution, echoing similar sentiments by his Estonian
counterpart.  The situation “when some countries have agreements on
collateral and some don’t isn’t a solution,” Miklos told
reporters in Bratislava today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Radoslav Tomek in Bratislava at 
 rtomek@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  